{"id": 8423, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "HL", "paper": "1", "year": "2022", "session": "22M", "subtopic": "21-1-spectroscopic-identification-of-organic-compounds", "title": "22M.1.HL.TZ1.38", "topic_id": "21", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>Which compound produces the following <sup>1</sup>H NMR spectrum?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"/></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><sup>[Spectral Database for Organic Compounds, SDBS. SDBS Compounds and Spectral Search. [graph] Available at:</sup><br/><sup>https://sdbs.db.aist.go.jp [Accessed 3 January 2019].]</sup></p>\n<p><br/>A.  propanal</p>\n<p>B.  propanone</p>\n<p>C.  propane</p>\n<p>D.  methlypropane</p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>A majority of students identified the correct compound for the <sup>1</sup>H NMR spectrum given.</p>\n</div>"}